'''Simon Dalby''' is an Irish born<ref>{{cite web|title=Faculty Profiles - Simon Dalby|url=https://www.wlu.ca/faculty-profiles/arts/simon-dalby.html|website=WLU.ca|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020170643/https://www.wlu.ca/faculty-profiles/arts/simon-dalby.html|archivedate=2016-10-20|df=}}</ref> academic and [[Centre for International Governance Innovation|CIGI]] Chair in the Political Economy of Climate Change at the [[Balsillie School of International Affairs]]. Dalby works in the disciplines of [[environmental security]] and [[critical geopolitics]].
